    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already feel 100% better. isn't the whole point of the medicine to get rid of the infection? if the symptoms are gone, it means the bacteria are dead, right? i'm just worried about the side effects of taking more than i actually need. it feels kinda unnecessary at this point.",
